<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Advocate Sumit Birthday ❤️⚖️</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
height:100vh;
overflow:hidden;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff4da6,#ff85c2,#ffc0cb);
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
color:white;
position:relative;
}

.page{
display:none;
width:90%;
max-width:750px;
padding:40px;
border-radius:30px;
text-align:center;
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
backdrop-filter:blur(15px);
box-shadow:0 0 35px rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
animation:fade 1s ease;
}

.active{
display:block;
}

@keyframes fade{
from{
opacity:0;
transform:scale(0.9);
}
to{
opacity:1;
transform:scale(1);
}
}

h1{
font-size:3rem;
margin-bottom:15px;
text-shadow:0 0 15px white;
}

h2{
margin-top:20px;
color:#fff5f8;
}

p{
margin-top:18px;
font-size:1.15rem;
line-height:1.8;
}

.btn{
margin-top:30px;
padding:14px 28px;
border:none;
border-radius:50px;
font-size:1rem;
font-weight:bold;
cursor:pointer;
transition:0.3s;
}

.yes{
background:white;
color:#ff1493;
}

.yes:hover{
transform:scale(1.1);
box-shadow:0 0 20px white;
}

.no{
background:#ffb6d9;
color:white;
cursor:not-allowed;
opacity:0.5;
}

.heart{
position:absolute;
bottom:-10px;
font-size:25px;
animation:float 6s linear infinite;
opacity:0.7;
}

@keyframes float{
0%{
transform:translateY(0);
opacity:0;
}
100%{
transform:translateY(-110vh);
opacity:1;
}
}

.glitter{
position:absolute;
width:5px;
height:5px;
background:white;
border-radius:50%;
animation:sparkle 2s infinite;
}

@keyframes sparkle{
0%{
opacity:0;
transform:scale(0);
}
50%{
opacity:1;
transform:scale(1);
}
100%{
opacity:0;
transform:scale(0);
}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- PAGE 1 -->
<div class="page active" id="page1">

<h1>🎂 Happy Birthday 🎂</h1>

<h2>Advocate Sumit ⚖️❤️</h2>

<p>
Happy Birthday to the only advocate who can easily win arguments…
and my attention too 😌⚖️❤️
</p>

<p>
To my favorite advocate —
if charm was a court case,
you’d win every single hearing without evidence 😌⚖️
</p>

<p>
“You defend clients in court…
but who’s going to defend me from your smile?” 😌⚖️❤️
</p>

<p>
“Objection your honor…
he’s illegally attractive 🫣⚖️”
</p>

<button class="btn yes" onclick="nextPage(2)">
Open Your Birthday Case File 💌
</button>

</div>



<!-- PAGE 2 -->
<div class="page" id="page2">

<h1>⚖️ Special Hearing ⚖️</h1>

<p>
“If loving your attention was a crime,
I’d happily confess 😌❤️”
</p>

<p>
“You don’t just win court cases…
you quietly win hearts too ⚖️✨”
</p>

<p>
“Your arguments are strong…
but your charm is stronger 😌⚖️”
</p>

<p>
“I think you cross-examined my heart without permission ❤️”
</p>

<p>
⚖️ Advocate Sumit —
professionally dangerous in court
and personally dangerous to my focus 😭❤️
</p>

<button class="btn yes" onclick="nextPage(3)">
Continue ❤️
</button>

</div>



<!-- PAGE 3 -->
<div class="page" id="page3">

<h1>💖 Important Question 💖</h1>

<p style="font-size:1.5rem;">
Would you like to spend your precious time with me...? 😌❤️
</p>

<button class="btn yes" onclick="nextPage(4)">
YES ❤️
</button>

<button class="btn no">
NO ❌
</button>

</div>



<!-- PAGE 4 -->
<div class="page" id="page4">

<h1>🥹❤️ Final Verdict ❤️</h1>

<p style="font-size:1.4rem;">
I knew your answer would be YES 😌⚖️
</p>

<p>
⚖️ Happy Birthday to the man who can win every case with logic…
and steal hearts without even trying 😌❤️
</p>

<p>
❤️ Some people argue to win cases…
you just smile and automatically win people 😌⚖️
</p>

<p>
⚖️ If birthdays were court hearings,
today’s judgment is officially in your favor 😌✨
</p>

<p>
❤️ Even the strongest arguments lose against your smile ⚖️✨
</p>

<p>
🎂 Wishing the most elegant advocate endless happiness,
success and beautiful memories ❤️✨
</p>

<h2>
Happy Birthday Again Advocate Sumit ⚖️❤️
</h2>

</div>



<script>

function nextPage(page){
document.querySelectorAll('.page').forEach(p=>{
p.classList.remove('active');
});

document.getElementById('page'+page).classList.add('active');
}

function createHeart(){
const heart=document.createElement('div');

heart.classList.add('heart');
heart.innerHTML='❤️';

heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+'vw';
heart.style.animationDuration=(Math.random()*3+3)+'s';

document.body.appendChild(heart);

setTimeout(()=>{
heart.remove();
},6000);
}

setInterval(createHeart,300);

function createGlitter(){
const glitter=document.createElement('div');

glitter.classList.add('glitter');

glitter.style.left=Math.random()*100+'vw';
glitter.style.top=Math.random()*100+'vh';

document.body.appendChild(glitter);

setTimeout(()=>{
glitter.remove();
},2000);
}

setInterval(createGlitter,150);

</script>

</body>
</html>
